data.description: Rare Find! Below market value! Only mins to Charlottesville! Discover a Slice of Paradise! Embrace the Exclusivity. The prop may be able to be subdivided to build another house An Unmatched 6.75 Acres of Untouched Serenity and Splendor! Find Your Haven of Peace, Quiet and Ultimate Relaxation!  Feel the timeless charm radiate from the older farmhouse that graces this remarkable property. Journey down your very own private driveway, leading you to a world of unrivaled beauty. And the best part? You're just minutes away from the vibrant city of Charlottesville, ensuring convenience without compromising the tranquility you crave. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a piece of heaven on earth—seize the moment and make this extraordinary retreat your very own!
